# Netflix Clone Multi-Agent Project

## Architecture Blueprint
- /frontend: React.js + Tailwind CSS (UI & Video Player)
- /backend: Node.js + Express (Authentication & Video APIs)
- /streaming-server: HLS/FFmpeg (Video transcoding & distribution)

## Agent Allocation
- Agent 1 (UI/UX Explorer): Responsible for Frontend setup.
- Agent 2 (DB & Auth Specialist): Responsible for Backend & MongoDB setup.
- Agent 3 (Media Streaming Expert): Responsible for HLS Video Pipeline.
